\begin{abstract}
 We prove a sharp moment inequality for a log-concave or a log-convex function, 
 on Gaussian random vectors. As an application we take a stability result for the 
 classical logarithmic Sobolev inequality of L. Gross in the case where the function 
 is log-concave. 
\end{abstract}





